"{\"uid\": \"hindustantimes.com-world-news-us-news-adidas-says-sorry-to-bella-hadid-and-partners-over-munich-olympics-campaign-after-facing-legal-threat-101721635407752.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 14, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get features like  Adidas is once again in damage control mode, issuing a public apology over their controversialMunich Olympicscampaign.\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 40, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.807688621997237e-16, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just three days after initial backlash, the German sportswear giant is extending its mea culpa.\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9913349991043597, \"rank\": 0.007926180907653716, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, they are acknowledging the unintended offence caused and expressing regret directly to their campaign partners, including supermodel Bella Hadid.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 393, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bella Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adidasissued a second apology on Sunday regarding their SL72 campaign, which referenced the 1972 Munich Olympics.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company acknowledged that despite removingpro-Palestinianmodel Bella Hadid, from the campaign, some continue to draw unintentional links between the ad and the tragic historical event.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bella Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Connections continue to be made to the terrible tragedy that occurred at the Munich Olympics due to our recent SL72 campaign,\\\" the brand wrote.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These connections are not meant and we apologise for any upset or distress caused to communities around the world,\\\" they further added.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the unversed, The Munich Olympics are remembered for a tragic incident where 11 Israeli athletes were kidnapped and killed by the Palestinian terrorist group \\\"Black September.\\\"\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4702553048122517e-19, \"text\": \"Munich Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\"}, {\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.8694193058105268, \"rank\": 0.11216529484848183, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}, {\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9998061515343302, \"rank\"