ess\"}, {\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999990449064184, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jules Kound\\u00e9\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The footwear brand landed in hot water after receiving backlash from Jewish groups and Israel for featuring supermodelBella Hadidin its latest campaign for retro-styled sneakers.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9999332225571335, \"rank\": 6.482104420836202e-05, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}, {\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.372692547973207e-12, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adidas subsequently removed Hadid, who has Palestinian roots and has been a prominent advocate for Palestinian relief efforts.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9998061515343302, \"rank\": 0.00014885975918221074, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 1764, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9998061515343302, \"rank\": 0.00014885975918221074, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are aware that connections have been made to tragic historical events - though these are completely unintentional - and we apologize for any upset or distress caused,\\\" a spokesperson for Adidas said in a statement sent to CNN on Friday.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.807688621997237e-16, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}, {\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.937355669111452e-13, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also read:Ben Affleck and Jennifer Lopez 'not getting back together,' but the plans to split are\\u2026  The brand with global appeal also promised to revise the campaign and reinforce its belief in sport as a unifying force.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Affleck\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Affleck\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Affleck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Affleck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We \\\"will continue our efforts to champion diversity and equality in everything we do,\\\" the company added.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After getting rid of all Bella Hadid ads, the brand got a new round of backlash from pro-Palestinian groups.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bella Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These groups alleged that the brand was engaging in silencing tactics against voices of Palestinian heritage and retaliating against Hadid in response to her heritage.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2558, \"end\": 2569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9998061515343302, \"rank\": 0.00014885975918221074, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to sources reported by TMZ, Bella Hadid has engaged the services of a legal representative to pursue legal action against the German brand.\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.383406846296215e-18, \"text\": \"TMZ\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\"}, {\"begin\": 2677, \"end\": 2688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bella Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}, {\"begin\": 2775, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9913349991043597, \"rank\": 0.007926180907653716, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She expressed dissatisfaction with the company for failing to assume accountability and for conducting a detrimental marketing campaign.\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid, the daughter of Palestinian-American real-estate developer Mohamed Hadid, has consistently advocated for her heritage.\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinian_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Palestinian-American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinian_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinian_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 3006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mohamed Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Hadid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has made numerous public statements regarding the violence faced by Palestinians and the protracted conflict in Gaza.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3125, \"end\": 3137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9999754242935878, \"rank\": 2.4425154222146044e-05, \"text\": \"Palestinians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 3169, \"end\": 3173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9999901965282664, \"rank\": 9.803567983872404e-06, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My heart is bleeding with pain from the trauma I am seeing unfold, as well as the generational trauma of my Palestinian blood,\\\" she wrote back in October last year.\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3285, \"end\": 3296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9998061515343302, \"rank\": 0.00014885975918221074, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I mourn for the Israeli families that have been dealing with the pain and aftermath of October 7,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3359, \"end\": 3366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.8694193058105268, \"rank\": 0.11216529484848183, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}]}]}"